999. BMJ Open. 2021 Dec 6;11(12):e052156. doi: 10.1136/bmjopen-2021-052156.

Economic evaluation of an Australian nurse home visiting programme: a randomised 
trial at 3 years.

Bohingamu Mudiyanselage S(1), Price AMH(2)(3)(4), Mensah FK(2)(4), Bryson 
HE(2)(3), Perlen S(2)(3), Orsini F(5)(6), Hiscock H(3), Dakin P(7), Harris D(7), 
Noble K(7), Bruce T(8), Kemp L(8), Goldfeld S(2)(3)(4), Gold L(9).

Author information:
